{"id":"datalinq-helper-table","name":null,"description":null,"code":"<div class=\"navbar\">\r\n  <div class=\"title\" id=\"function-title\"><a href=\"https://localhost:7277/datalinq/report/datalinq-guide@select-all-users@index\">DataLinq-Helper: Table</a></div>\r\n  <div style=\"width: 30px;\"></div> \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n\r\n<button class=\"collapsible\">\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-label\">Basic Usage all records</span>\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-actions\">\r\n        <span class=\"action-button\" onclick=\"openPopup(event, 'table_allRecords')\">Code/Query</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n</button>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n    @DLH.Table(Model.Records)\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"description_table_allRecords\" hidden>\r\nde: Die Funktion Table(Model.Records) erstellt eine formatierte Tabelle, \r\ndie alle Zeilen und Spalten des übergebenen Datenmodells anzeigt. \r\nDas Layout folgt einem vordefinierten Stil zur konsistenten Darstellung.\r\n\r\nen: The function Table(Model.Records) creates a formatted table displaying \r\nall rows and columns of the provided data model. \r\nThe layout follows a predefined style for consistent presentation.\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"csharp_table_allRecords\" hidden><script type=\"text/plain\">@@DLH.Table(Model.Records)</script></div>\r\n<div id=\"sql_table_allRecords\" hidden>SELECT * FROM Users WHERE 0 = 0</div>\r\n\r\n<button class=\"collapsible\">\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-label\">Limit record count</span>\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-actions\">\r\n        <span class=\"action-button\" onclick=\"openPopup(event, 'table_limitedRecordCount')\">Code/Query</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n</button>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n    @DLH.Table(Model.Records, max: 10)\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"description_table_limitedRecordCount\" hidden>\r\nde: Der Parameter \"max\" begrenzt die Anzahl der geladenen Zeilen. \r\nIn diesem Fall werden maximal 100 Datensätze angezeigt.\r\n\r\nen: The \"max\" parameter limits the number of rows being loaded. \r\nIn this case, a maximum of 100 records will be displayed.\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"csharp_table_limitedRecordCount\" hidden><script type=\"text/plain\">@@DLH.Table(Model.Records, max: 10)</script></div>\r\n<div id=\"sql_table_limitedRecordCount\" hidden>SELECT * FROM Users WHERE 0 = 0</div>\r\n<button class=\"collapsible\">\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-label\">Only selected Columns</span>\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-actions\">\r\n        <span class=\"action-button\" onclick=\"openPopup(event, 'table_selectedColumns')\">Code/Query</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n</button>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n    @DLH.Table(Model.Records, columns:[\"FirstName\",\"LastName\"])\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"description_table_selectedColumns\" hidden>\r\nde: Der Parameter \"columns\" ermöglicht die gezielte Auswahl bestimmter Spalten, \r\ndie in der Tabelle angezeigt werden sollen. \r\nIn diesem Fall: \"FirstName\" und \"LastName\".\r\n\r\nen: The \"columns\" parameter allows selecting specific columns to be displayed \r\nin the table. In this case: \"FirstName\" and \"LastName\".\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"csharp_table_selectedColumns\" hidden><script type=\"text/plain\">@@DLH.Table(Model.Records, columns:[\"FirstName\",\"LastName\"])</script></div>\r\n<div id=\"sql_table_selectedColumns\" hidden>SELECT * FROM Users WHERE 0 = 0</div>\r\n\r\n<button class=\"collapsible\">\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-label\">HTML Attributes</span>\r\n    <span class=\"collapsible-actions\">\r\n        <span class=\"action-button\" onclick=\"openPopup(event, 'table_htmlAttributes')\">Code/Query</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n</button>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n    @DLH.Table(\r\n    records: Model.Records, \r\n    htmlAttributes: new { style = \"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: sans-serif;\" }, \r\n    row0HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"background-color: #1e293b; color: white; text-align: left;\" }, \r\n    row1HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"background-color: #f8fafc;\" }, \r\n    row2HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"background-color: #e2e8f0;\" }, \r\n    cell0HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"padding: 12px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1;\" }, \r\n    cellHtmlAttributes: new { style = \"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1;\" }\r\n)\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"description_table_htmlAttributes\" hidden>\r\nde: Die Parameter \"htmlAttributes\", \"row0HtmlAttributes\", \"row1HtmlAttributes\", \"row2HtmlAttributes\", \"cell0HtmlAttributes\" und \"cellHtmlAttributes\" ermöglichen eine gezielte CSS-Anpassung der Tabelle. \r\n- \"htmlAttributes\": Stil für das gesamte table-Element (z. B. border-collapse, width)\r\n- \"row0HtmlAttributes\": Stil für die Kopfzeile (z. B. Hintergrundfarbe, Textausrichtung)\r\n- \"row1HtmlAttributes\": Stil für ungerade Datenzeilen (z. B. Hintergrundfarbe für Zebramuster)\r\n- \"row2HtmlAttributes\": Stil für gerade Datenzeilen (abwechselnde Darstellung)\r\n- \"cell0HtmlAttributes\": Stil für Zellen in der Kopfzeile (z. B. Schriftgewicht, Padding)\r\n- \"cellHtmlAttributes\": Stil für alle anderen Zellen (z. B. Rahmen, Schriftgröße)\r\n\r\nen: The parameters \"htmlAttributes\", \"row0HtmlAttributes\", \"row1HtmlAttributes\", \"row2HtmlAttributes\", \"cell0HtmlAttributes\", and \"cellHtmlAttributes\" allow fine-grained CSS styling of the table. \r\n- \"htmlAttributes\": styles for the table itself (e.g., border-collapse, width)\r\n- \"row0HtmlAttributes\": styles for the header row (e.g., background color, text alignment)\r\n- \"row1HtmlAttributes\": styles for odd data rows (e.g., zebra-striping background)\r\n- \"row2HtmlAttributes\": styles for even data rows (alternate display)\r\n- \"cell0HtmlAttributes\": styles for header cells (e.g., font weight, padding)\r\n- \"cellHtmlAttributes\": styles for all other cells (e.g., borders, font size)\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"csharp_table_htmlAttributes\" hidden><script type=\"text/plain\">\r\n@@DLH.Table(\r\n    records: Model.Records, \r\n    htmlAttributes: new { style = \"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: sans-serif;\" }, \r\n    row0HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"background-color: #1e293b; color: white; text-align: left;\" }, \r\n    row1HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"background-color: #f8fafc;\" }, \r\n    row2HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"background-color: #e2e8f0;\" }, \r\n    cell0HtmlAttributes: new { style = \"padding: 12px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1;\" }, \r\n    cellHtmlAttributes: new { style = \"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1;\" }\r\n)\r\n</script></div>\r\n<div id=\"sql_table_htmlAttributes\" hidden>SELECT * FROM Users WHERE 0 = 0</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n","created":"2025-04-14T07:06:58","changed":"2025-05-09T07:30:25.0460345Z","test_parameters":null,"included_js_libs":"legacy_chartjs"}